Description:
Ballistics of the Type 73 Universal HEAT-T shot (industrial designation WB122P) for the Type 73, 86 smoothbore anti-tank gun, Type 59 rifled-, and Type 69 smoothbore tank guns. Universal denotes compatibility with both rifled and smoothbore armaments. Type 69 is a smoothbore conversion of the Type 59 tank gun (domestic version of Soviet tank gun D-10), Type 73 employs the same barrel and ammo as Type 69 tank gun on the carriage of the Soviet field gun BS-3.
